{"type": "article", "id": 28631, "title": "木制电钢琴", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 74, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163704wcO0JUj8kzebVguE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>电子乐器制造商罗兰（<a href=\"http://www.roland.com/\">Roland</a>）与日本家具设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.karimoku-newstandard.jp/\">Karimoku</a> 联手推出纯手工制作的木制电钢琴 Kiyola KF-10，是一款将数码乐器与家居结合在一起的产品。它的饰面采用的是核桃木和纯橡木这样的低甲醛木材，不仅环保，也带来了赏心悦目的木质肌理花纹。Karimoku 还设计了一把符合人体工程学的钢琴凳：呈拱形的高密度坐垫能够更均匀地分布重量，减少久坐对身体造成的损伤。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163702ZNbFRVHxfgWYiqoK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021637038aYieORBdNLWoQpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163703htf3XSz8ULGC5JpE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163704DmsPWnpzuTe2EbQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}